    {
      "id": "p_farm_intro",
      "panelType": "text",
      "title": "Farming Overview",
      "content": "Check off crops as you grow them — useful for tracking the **Every Crop** and **Full Bloom** achievements.\n\n- **Re-growing crops** continue to produce after harvest each season; plant early for best value.\n- **Flowers** don't have quality tiers — only one sale price.\n- All tree seeds are available year-round from Souffle Farm or Taylor's Seeds (call 881).\n- **Days shown** are for Good quality soil. Decent soil adds 1–2 days; Good is standard."
    },
